        <div class="block-content">
         <div class="view view-homepage-mini-features view-id-homepage_mini_features view-display-id-block view-dom-id-ecbb7f59d65f16479d79f115a4fa4dc7">
          <div class="view-content">
           <div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first views-row-last">
            <article class="node-41 node node-homepage-mini-feature view-mode-full clearfix">
             <span>
              <img alt="" src="http://surgery.uchicago.edu/sites/surgery.uchicago.edu/files/styles/columnwidth-wider/public/uploads/images/Annual%20Report%202018%20cover.JPG?itok=PFBdr5Zf"/>
             </span>
             <h2>
              Learn More About our Faculty's Groundbreaking Achievements in the 2018 Annual Report
             </h2>
             <p>
              The Department of Surgery's 2018 Annual Report is now available. Learn about the extraordinary advances our faculty and surgeons are making in patient care, research and education.
              <a href="news/learn-more-about-department-surgery-constant">
